# QA Standards for BizCode

**Purpose:** Establish comprehensive testing strategies, quality gates, and testing best practices for BizCode production deployment.
**Scope:** Unit, integration, E2E, component, visual, accessibility, performance, security, and manual testing.
**Status:** Production-ready QA standards for 6-8 week implementation.

---

## 1. TEST STRATEGY & COVERAGE

### Standard: Comprehensive multi-layer testing with clear coverage targets

**Testing Pyramid:**
```
       Manual Testing (5%)
      ┌─────────────────┐
      │  E2E Tests      │  5-10% of tests
      │  (Playwright)   │  Validate critical paths
      │                 │  Time: slow, high value
      └────────┬────────┘
    Integration Tests (15-20%)
    ┌──────────────────────┐
    │  Integration Tests   │  15-20% of tests
    │  (Vitest + DB)       │  API, database, services
    │                      │  Time: medium, good value
    └──────────┬───────────┘
  Unit Tests (70-80%)
  ┌──────────────────────────┐
  │     Unit Tests           │  70-80% of tests
  │     (Vitest)             │  Individual functions
  │                          │  Time: fast, isolation
  └──────────────────────────┘
```

**Coverage Targets:**
- **Unit Tests:** ≥90% coverage for src/lib/*, server/* critical paths
- **Integration Tests:** ≥75% coverage for API routes, database operations
- **E2E Tests:** ≥6 critical user flows (login, create, edit, delete, error handling, RBAC)
- **Component Tests:** ≥75% coverage for interactive components
- **Visual Regression:** ≥95% of pages captured and baseline matched
- **Accessibility:** 100% automated a11y checks pass, zero critical violations
- **Performance:** P95 response time <500ms, error rate <0.1%
- **Security:** 100% SAST scan pass, DAST coverage on critical paths

**Coverage Calculation:**
```
Total Coverage = (Lines Covered / Lines Executable) × 100%

Acceptable:
├── src/lib/**         ≥90% (utilities, validation, helpers)
├── server/routes/**   ≥85% (API endpoints)
├── server/services/** ≥85% (business logic)
├── src/components/**  ≥75% (UI components)
├── src/pages/**       ≥60% (page orchestration)
└── src/contexts/**    ≥90% (state management)

NOT acceptable:
├── < 60% on any critical module
├── Test files (exclude from coverage)
└── Generated files (exclude from coverage)
```

**Validation Checklist:**
```
✓ `npm run test` runs all unit tests
✓ `npm run test:integration` runs API + database tests
✓ `npm run test:e2e` runs Playwright critical paths
✓ Coverage report generated in coverage/index.html
✓ No coverage decrease allowed in PRs
✓ All tests pass on CI before merge
```

